Class DistinctSortedAscElements

  • java.lang.Object
    • DistinctSortedAscElements

  • public class DistinctSortedAscElements
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a simple application that reads integers from the console, removes duplicates, and prints the result in ascending order. The application also prints the count of the numbers, the count of the distinct numbers, the minimum and the maximum number.
